      "content": "hey quick question, if im working with a dataset where one feature is age (0-100) and another is annual income (0-200000), why do i actually need to scale them before running a model like k-means or something using gradient descent? thanks",
      "source": "evaluator",
      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "hey quick question, if im working with a dataset where one feature is age (0-100) and another is annual income (0-200000), why do i actually need to scale them before running a model like k-means or something using gradient descent? thanks",
